admin.DodgeMessage:
Hello {{user}},
We've noticed you've dodged {{amount}} game(s) in the past 7 days.
While we understand that there may be reasons for this, it's important to uphold the spirit of sportsmanship in our community.
Dodging games not only disrupts the gaming experience for others but also undermines the integrity of fair play.
We encourage you to approach each match with enthusiasm and commitment.
If this was a mistake or you need to remove a record, please contact us.
Best regards,
The Devs
